7. Design experiments that will produce ICMP messages of the following
type in a packet trace.
(1) Type 0, code 0
(2) Type 3, code 3
(3) Type 8, code 0
Ans:

(1) sudo tcpdump -w 1.cap -i eth0 dst 172.16.58.32
	 
(2)  sudo tcpdump -w 2.cap -i eth0 icmp
ping 172.16.19.203 -p 51543
     
(3) sudo tcpdump -w 3.cap -i eth0 src 172.16.58.126

